main event: Sightings of unidentified flying objects over England Air Force Base, Louisiana in November 1960
interesting points: Multiple unidentified objects were spotted, including round, white objects and disc-shaped objects around 10-15 feet in diameter.
The objects were observed maneuvering at high speeds, with erratic movements and the ability to hover or disappear suddenly.
Radar confirmed the visual sightings of the objects.
Interceptor aircraft were dispatched to investigate the sightings, but were unable to regain visual contact with the objects.
The sightings lasted for durations ranging from 30 seconds to several minutes.
